Overview

･WebGL version of the vehicle simulator currently under developmen

･TimeAttack is UI only and not yet implemented (to be implemented soon)

How to play

･Engine on/off: T

･Gas / Brake pedal: Up arrow / Down arrow

･Shift Up / Down: Q / E

･Clutch: C

･Change camera: Z

･Handle: Left arrow / Right arrow
